      "writtenOn": "2017-07-14T08:08:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It gets defined by this same class a few lines above in emitWind, so the base class can\u0027t really pass it into the function.\n\nI\u0027m also not a fan of littering these strings with %s, for the sake of readability.\n\nDoes this change with the more descriptive name and comment seem sufficient for you?",
