      "writtenOn": "2017-07-14T13:34:39Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It is better, but I still think you should just make a string that you pass around to the functions. Otherwise if you ever change the name/string you use or how you set up the functions, etc. it has to be updated everywhere.",
      "parentUuid": "70bb6845_e80c49ee",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 98,
        "startChar": 42,
        "endLine": 98,
        "endChar": 43
      },
      "revId": "e35a43a69b0fea2b721ff548e84917eb2395257b",
